{"id": "figure_003", "modality": "figures", "name": "GAN Generator + Discriminator", "task": {"description": "Create a single 1920x1080 self-contained HTML file using ONLY inline CSS and inline SVG that reproduces a GAN training figure with both networks. Title 'Generative Adversarial Network' at top in 32px bold. LEFT: a latent noise vector box 'z ~ N(0,1), 100-d' feeding into a 'Generator G' box (drawn as an upsampling trapezoid or stacked deconv boxes), producing a 'Fake Sample x_fake' box. A separate 'Real Sample x_real' box sits below/parallel. BOTH x_fake and x_real feed RIGHTWARD into a single 'Discriminator D' box (drawn as a downsampling trapezoid), which outputs a 'Real / Fake' probability box. Draw a labelled feedback arrow 'gradient / adversarial loss' curving from the Discriminator output BACK to the Generator. Annotate the two loss terms: 'D maximizes log D(x)' and 'G minimizes log(1 - D(G(z)))'. The real-sample arrow and the fake-sample arrow must both reach the Discriminator without crossing each other through any box. HARDEN (density + alignment): ALSO include (a) a LEGEND box that maps every distinct block color and every arrow/line style used in the figure, and (b) a small tensor-shape annotation on each major block (e.g. 'BxNxd'). Pack the figure densely with at least 14 labeled elements; every group of sibling blocks must be equal-size and share edges, with uniform gutters, and nothing may overlap or clip.", "requirements": ["All boxes (z, Generator G, x_fake, x_real, Discriminator D, Real/Fake output) are visible within the 1920x1080 viewport with no clipping at any edge", "No two boxes overlap each other", "Every box label text is fully contained inside its shape with no overflow", "The x_fake arrow and the x_real arrow both connect into the Discriminator D and neither passes through an unrelated box", "The feedback/adversarial-loss arrow runs from the Discriminator output back to the Generator and does not pass through the Discriminator or sample boxes", "The two loss-term annotations are both present, legible, and do not overlap any box or each other", "The 'z ~ N(0,1), 100-d' latent annotation is legible and inside its box", "Generator and Discriminator are visually distinguishable as up- vs down-sampling shapes (trapezoid or stack) and do not overlap", "No element is within 10px of any viewport edge", "No horizontal or vertical scrollbar appears; all content fits inside 1920x1080", "A legend box maps every block color and arrow/line style used; each major block carries a tensor-shape annotation; sibling blocks are equal-size and edge-aligned with uniform gutters; no element overlaps or is clipped"]}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 5138, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 2, "rv_total_tokens": 14855}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 5776, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 5895}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 4844, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 5677}], "ss_img": "images/figures/figure_003_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/figures/figure_003_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Generative Adversarial Network</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 20px;\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n        .title {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"title\">Generative Adversarial Network</div>\n        \n        <svg width=\"1880\" height=\"1000\" viewBox=\"0 0 1880 1000\">\n            <!-- Background -->\n            <rect width=\"1880\" height=\"1000\" fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#e0e0e0\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Generator Section Background -->\n            <rect x=\"50\" y=\"50\" width=\"600\" height=\"700\" fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"10\"/>\n            <text x=\"350\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2980b9\">Generator Network</text>\n            \n            <!-- Discriminator Section Background -->\n            <rect x=\"750\" y=\"50\" width=\"600\" height=\"700\" fill=\"#fdf2e8\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"10\"/>\n            <text x=\"1050\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#d35400\">Discriminator Network</text>\n            \n            <!-- Legend Box -->\n            <rect x=\"1400\" y=\"50\" width=\"430\" height=\"350\" fill=\"#f8f9fa\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"1615\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">LEGEND</text>\n            \n            <!-- Legend Items -->\n            <rect x=\"1420\" y=\"100\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#3498db\"/>\n            <text x=\"1460\" y=\"115\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Generator Components</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1420\" y=\"130\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#e67e22\"/>\n            <text x=\"1460\" y=\"145\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Discriminator Components</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1420\" y=\"160\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#27ae60\"/>\n            <text x=\"1460\" y=\"175\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Data Samples</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1420\" y=\"190\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#8e44ad\"/>\n            <text x=\"1460\" y=\"205\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Input Noise</text>\n            \n            <line x1=\"1420\" y1=\"225\" x2=\"1450\" y2=\"225\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"1460\" y=\"230\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Data Flow</text>\n            \n            <line x1=\"1420\" y1=\"250\" x2=\"1450\" y2=\"250\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\"/>\n            <text x=\"1460\" y=\"255\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Gradient Flow</text>\n            \n            <circle cx=\"1435\" cy=\"275\" r=\"8\" fill=\"#f39c12\"/>\n            <text x=\"1460\" y=\"280\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Loss Functions</text>\n            \n            <!-- Latent Noise Vector -->\n            <rect x=\"100\" y=\"150\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#8e44ad\" stroke=\"#6c3483\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"160\" y=\"175\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Latent Noise</text>\n            <text x=\"160\" y=\"190\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">z ~ N(0,1)</text>\n            <text x=\"160\" y=\"205\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">100-d</text>\n            <text x=\"160\" y=\"220\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#e8e8e8\">Bx100</text>\n            \n            <!-- Generator Network (Upsampling Trapezoid) -->\n            <polygon points=\"280,120 480,120 520,280 240,280\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"380\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Generator G</text>\n            <text x=\"380\" y=\"200\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">Deconv Layers</text>\n            <text x=\"380\" y=\"220\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">Upsampling</text>\n            <text x=\"380\" y=\"240\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#e8e8e8\">Bx3x64x64</text>\n            \n            <!-- Generator Sub-layers -->\n            <rect x=\"300\" y=\"140\" width=\"60\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#5dade2\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"330\" y=\"157\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"white\">FC</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"380\" y=\"140\" width=\"60\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#5dade2\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"410\" y=\"157\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"white\">Conv2D</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"460\" y=\"140\" width=\"60\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#5dade2\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"490\" y=\"157\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"white\">Upsample</text>\n            \n            <!-- Fake Sample -->\n            <rect x=\"550\" y=\"300\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"610\" y=\"325\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Fake Sample</text>\n            <text x=\"610\" y=\"340\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">x_fake</text>\n            <text x=\"610\" y=\"355\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">Generated</text>\n            <text x=\"610\" y=\"370\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#e8e8e8\">Bx3x64x64</text>\n            \n            <!-- Real Sample -->\n            <rect x=\"550\" y=\"450\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"610\" y=\"475\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Real Sample</text>\n            <text x=\"610\" y=\"490\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">x_real</text>\n            <text x=\"610\" y=\"505\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">Training Data</text>\n            <text x=\"610\" y=\"520\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#e8e8e8\">Bx3x64x64</text>\n            \n            <!-- Discriminator Network (Downsampling Trapezoid) -->\n            <polygon points=\"800,300 1000,300 960,500 840,500\" fill=\"#e67e22\" stroke=\"#d35400\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"900\" y=\"380\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Discriminator D</text>\n            <text x=\"900\" y=\"400\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">Conv Layers</text>\n            <text x=\"900\" y=\"420\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">Downsampling</text>\n            <text x=\"900\" y=\"440\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#e8e8e8\">Bx1</text>\n            \n            <!-- Discriminator Sub-layers -->\n            <rect x=\"820\" y=\"320\" width=\"50\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"845\" y=\"337\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"white\">Conv</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"880\" y=\"320\" width=\"50\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"905\" y=\"337\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"white\">Pool</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"940\" y=\"320\" width=\"50\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"965\" y=\"337\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"white\">FC</text>\n            \n            <!-- Real/Fake Output -->\n            <rect x=\"1050\" y=\"370\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"1110\" y=\"395\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Output</text>\n            <text x=\"1110\" y=\"410\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">Real / Fake</text>\n            <text x=\"1110\" y=\"425\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">Probability</text>\n            <text x=\"1110\" y=\"440\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#e8e8e8\">Bx1</text>\n            \n            <!-- Loss Function Annotations -->\n            <circle cx=\"1200\" cy=\"300\" r=\"15\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"1200\" y=\"306\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">L1</text>\n            <text x=\"1200\" y=\"270\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">D maximizes</text>\n            <text x=\"1200\" y=\"255\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">log D(x)</text>\n            \n            <circle cx=\"1200\" cy=\"500\" r=\"15\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"1200\" y=\"506\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">L2</text>\n            <text x=\"1200\" y=\"530\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">G minimizes</text>\n            <text x=\"1200\" y=\"545\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">log(1 - D(G(z)))</text>\n            \n            <!-- Data Flow Arrows -->\n            <!-- Noise to Generator -->\n            <line x1=\"220\" y1=\"190\" x2=\"280\" y2=\"190\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Generator to Fake Sample -->\n            <line x1=\"520\" y1=\"280\" x2=\"550\" y2=\"320\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Fake Sample to Discriminator -->\n            <line x1=\"670\" y1=\"340\" x2=\"800\" y2=\"360\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Real Sample to Discriminator -->\n            <line x1=\"670\" y1=\"490\" x2=\"800\" y2=\"440\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Discriminator to Output -->\n            <line x1=\"1000\" y1=\"400\" x2=\"1050\" y2=\"410\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Gradient Feedback Arrow (curved) -->\n            <path d=\"M 1110 370 Q 1250 200 400 100\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n            <text x=\"800\" y=\"120\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" font-weight=\"bold\">Gradient / Adversarial Loss</text>\n            \n            <!-- Training Process Annotations -->\n            <rect x=\"100\" y=\"600\" width=\"500\" height=\"120\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#95a5a6\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"350\" y=\"630\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Training Process</text>\n            <text x=\"120\" y=\"655\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">1. Train D: Maximize log D(x_real) + log(1 - D(G(z)))</text>\n            <text x=\"120\" y=\"675\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">2. Train G: Minimize log(1 - D(G(z)))</text>\n            <text x=\"120\" y=\"695\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">3. Alternate between steps 1 and 2</text>\n            \n            <!-- Network Architecture Details -->\n            <rect x=\"750\" y=\"600\" width=\"500\" height=\"120\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#95a5a6\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"1000\" y=\"630\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Architecture Details</text>\n            <text x=\"770\" y=\"655\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Generator: FC \u2192 Conv2D \u2192 BatchNorm \u2192 ReLU \u2192 Upsample</text>\n            <text x=\"770\" y=\"675\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Discriminator: Conv2D \u2192 LeakyReLU \u2192 Dropout \u2192 FC \u2192 Sigmoid</text>\n            <text x=\"770\" y=\"695\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Batch Size: B, Image: 3\u00d764\u00d764, Latent: 100-d</text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow Markers -->\n            <defs>\n                <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                </marker>\n                <marker id=\"arrowhead-red\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#e74c3c\"/>\n                </marker>\n            </defs>\n        </svg>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Generative Adversarial Network</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 20px;\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n        .title {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .main-content {\n            flex: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 40px;\n        }\n        .diagram-area {\n            flex: 3;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        .legend-area {\n            flex: 1;\n            background: white;\n            border: 2px solid #34495e;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n        .legend-title {\n            font-size: 18px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .legend-item {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            margin-bottom: 12px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            color: #34495e;\n        }\n        .legend-color {\n            width: 20px;\n            height: 20px;\n            margin-right: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid #7f8c8d;\n        }\n        .legend-line {\n            width: 30px;\n            height: 2px;\n            margin-right: 10px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"title\">Generative Adversarial Network</div>\n        \n        <div class=\"main-content\">\n            <div class=\"diagram-area\">\n                <svg width=\"1400\" height=\"900\" viewBox=\"0 0 1400 900\">\n                    <!-- Background -->\n                    <rect width=\"1400\" height=\"900\" fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#e0e0e0\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"10\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- Latent Noise Vector -->\n                    <rect x=\"50\" y=\"150\" width=\"180\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"140\" y=\"175\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Latent Noise</text>\n                    <text x=\"140\" y=\"195\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">z ~ N(0,1)</text>\n                    <text x=\"140\" y=\"210\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">Shape: Bx100</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Generator Network (Upsampling Trapezoid) -->\n                    <polygon points=\"280,120 480,120 520,260 240,260\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n                    <text x=\"380\" y=\"185\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Generator G</text>\n                    <text x=\"380\" y=\"205\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">Upsampling</text>\n                    <text x=\"380\" y=\"220\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">Shape: Bx3x64x64</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Generator Layers -->\n                    <rect x=\"290\" y=\"140\" width=\"40\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#2980b9\" stroke=\"#1f4e79\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n                    <text x=\"310\" y=\"153\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"white\">FC</text>\n                    <rect x=\"340\" y=\"140\" width=\"40\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#2980b9\" stroke=\"#1f4e79\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n                    <text x=\"360\" y=\"153\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"white\">Conv</text>\n                    <rect x=\"390\" y=\"140\" width=\"40\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#2980b9\" stroke=\"#1f4e79\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n                    <text x=\"410\" y=\"153\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"white\">Conv</text>\n                    <rect x=\"440\" y=\"140\" width=\"40\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#2980b9\" stroke=\"#1f4e79\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n                    <text x=\"460\" y=\"153\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"white\">Conv</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Fake Sample -->\n                    <rect x=\"570\" y=\"150\" width=\"180\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"660\" y=\"175\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Fake Sample</text>\n                    <text x=\"660\" y=\"195\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">x_fake</text>\n                    <text x=\"660\" y=\"210\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">Shape: Bx3x64x64</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Real Sample -->\n                    <rect x=\"570\" y=\"350\" width=\"180\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"660\" y=\"375\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Real Sample</text>\n                    <text x=\"660\" y=\"395\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">x_real</text>\n                    <text x=\"660\" y=\"410\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">Shape: Bx3x64x64</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Discriminator Network (Downsampling Trapezoid) -->\n                    <polygon points=\"820,120 1020,120 1060,460 780,460\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n                    <text x=\"920\" y=\"275\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Discriminator D</text>\n                    <text x=\"920\" y=\"295\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">Downsampling</text>\n                    <text x=\"920\" y=\"310\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">Shape: Bx1</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Discriminator Layers -->\n                    <rect x=\"830\" y=\"140\" width=\"40\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#8e44ad\" stroke=\"#6c3483\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n                    <text x=\"850\" y=\"153\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"white\">Conv</text>\n                    <rect x=\"880\" y=\"180\" width=\"40\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#8e44ad\" stroke=\"#6c3483\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n                    <text x=\"900\" y=\"193\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"white\">Conv</text>\n                    <rect x=\"930\" y=\"220\" width=\"40\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#8e44ad\" stroke=\"#6c3483\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n                    <text x=\"950\" y=\"233\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"white\">Conv</text>\n                    <rect x=\"980\" y=\"260\" width=\"40\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#8e44ad\" stroke=\"#6c3483\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n                    <text x=\"1000\" y=\"273\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"white\">FC</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Real/Fake Output -->\n                    <rect x=\"1110\" y=\"250\" width=\"180\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#34495e\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"1200\" y=\"275\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Real / Fake</text>\n                    <text x=\"1200\" y=\"295\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">Probability</text>\n                    <text x=\"1200\" y=\"310\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">Shape: Bx1</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Arrows -->\n                    <!-- Noise to Generator -->\n                    <path d=\"M 230 190 L 240 190\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- Generator to Fake Sample -->\n                    <path d=\"M 520 190 L 570 190\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- Fake Sample to Discriminator -->\n                    <path d=\"M 750 190 L 780 190\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- Real Sample to Discriminator -->\n                    <path d=\"M 750 390 L 780 390\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- Discriminator to Output -->\n                    <path d=\"M 1060 290 L 1110 290\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- Feedback Arrow (Curved) -->\n                    <path d=\"M 1200 250 Q 1300 150 1300 100 Q 1300 50 900 50 Q 500 50 380 120\" \n                          stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"4\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"8,4\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n                    <text x=\"900\" y=\"40\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#e74c3c\">Gradient / Adversarial Loss</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Loss Annotations -->\n                    <rect x=\"50\" y=\"500\" width=\"300\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"200\" y=\"520\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Discriminator Loss</text>\n                    <text x=\"200\" y=\"540\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">D maximizes log D(x_real) + log(1 - D(x_fake))</text>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"400\" y=\"500\" width=\"300\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"550\" y=\"520\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Generator Loss</text>\n                    <text x=\"550\" y=\"540\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">G minimizes log(1 - D(G(z)))</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Training Process -->\n                    <rect x=\"750\" y=\"500\" width=\"200\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"850\" y=\"520\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Training Process</text>\n                    <text x=\"850\" y=\"540\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Alternating optimization</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Objective -->\n                    <rect x=\"1000\" y=\"500\" width=\"300\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"1150\" y=\"520\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Minimax Objective</text>\n                    <text x=\"1150\" y=\"540\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">min_G max_D V(D,G)</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Arrow markers -->\n                    <defs>\n                        <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                            <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        </marker>\n                        <marker id=\"arrowhead-red\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                            <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#e74c3c\"/>\n                        </marker>\n                    </defs>\n                </svg>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"legend-area\">\n                <div class=\"legend-title\">Legend</div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background-color: #e74c3c;\"></div>\n                    <span>Latent Input</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background-color: #3498db;\"></div>\n                    <span>Generator Network</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background-color: #f39c12;\"></div>\n                    <span>Generated Data</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background-color: #27ae60;\"></div>\n                    <span>Real Data</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background-color: #9b59b6;\"></div>\n                    <span>Discriminator Network</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background-color: #34495e;\"></div>\n                    <span>Classification Output</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background-color: #ecf0f1;\"></div>\n                    <span>Loss Functions</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-line\" style=\"background-color: #2c3e50; height: 3px;\"></div>\n                    <span>Data Flow</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-line\" style=\"background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, #e74c3c 0px, #e74c3c 8px, transparent 8px, transparent 12px); height: 4px;\"></div>\n                    <span>Gradient Flow</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div style=\"margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #bdc3c7;\">\n                    <div style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #7f8c8d; line-height: 1.4;\">\n                        <strong>Tensor Shapes:</strong><br>\n                        B = Batch size<br>\n                        100 = Latent dimension<br>\n                        3x64x64 = RGB image<br>\n                        1 = Scalar probability\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>"}